### ===============================
### /items/  (Query Param Models)
### ===============================

### ✅ OK: sin query (usa defaults)
### - limit=100, offset=0, order_by="created_at", tags=[]
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/
Accept: application/json


### ✅ OK: limit y offset válidos
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/?limit=20&offset=40
Accept: application/json


### ✅ OK: order_by válido (Literal)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/?order_by=updated_at
Accept: application/json


### ✅ OK: tags (lista) repetido en query
### Nota: se envía como tags=a&tags=b
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/?tags=fastapi&tags=react
Accept: application/json


### ✅ OK: combinación completa
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/?limit=10&offset=0&order_by=created_at&tags=api&tags=docs
Accept: application/json


### ❌ 422: limit debe ser > 0 (gt=0)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/?limit=0
Accept: application/json


### ❌ 422: limit debe ser <= 100 (le=100)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/?limit=101
Accept: application/json


### ❌ 422: offset debe ser >= 0 (ge=0)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/?offset=-1
Accept: application/json


### ❌ 422: order_by inválido (solo "created_at" o "updated_at")
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/?order_by=name
Accept: application/json


### ❌ 422: limit debe ser int (tipo incorrecto)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/?limit=abc
Accept: application/json
